						<dl><dd><i>For other ways of moving between two maps, see <a href="/web/20210512080836/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Map_transfers" title="Map transfers">Map transfers</a>.</i></dd></dl>
						<p>
							This page describes how to&nbsp;<b>connect maps together</b>&nbsp;seamlessly, so that the player can walk from one to the other.
						</p>
